ELTEX Company is a leading Russian designer and manufacturer of communication equipment. The company was founded in 1992.  ELTEX has more than 1800 employees.The company’s specialists carry out a full cycle of development and production, including the development of circuits, circuit board design, software and prototype development, and, finally, mass producing. Complex solutions and the possibility of their seamless integration into the customer’s infrastructure is a priority development direction of the enterprise.
Among the products developed by Eltex are: 
- GPON equipment
- Network equipment (Ethernet access, aggregation and core switches, service routers, firewalls);
- Voip Equipment (IP-PBXs , digital and voice gateways, SoftSwitch);
- Wi-Fi equipment (access points for outdoor and indoor use, Wi-Fi controllers);
- Smart home solution;
- Management and monitoring systems.

ShareID specializes in combating identity fraud, offering a modular platform for punctual and recurrent identity verification needs. Businesses can create the workflow that best suits their risk and compliance requirements through a single subscription: 

1. PUNCTUAL VERIFICATION: 
- Doc IDV: Available in Video AI and NFC for ID document authenticity;
- Liveness IDV: Active and passive liveness checks; 
- Full IDV: A combination of Doc IDV & Liveness IDV for onboarding with a possibility of reuse. 

2. RECURRENT VERIFICATION: 
- MFA 3.0: A multi-factor authentication solution with a simple smile. Can be also used for age verification 

3. DIGITAL IDENTITY VERIFICATION: 
- ANA: Anonymous authentication; 
- SENSA: Verified personal data sharing.

TSS is a prominent developer of advanced information security tools, specializing in the independent development of software and engineering solutions for comprehensive information security. 
Products: 
• Diamond VPN/FW – multi-functional UTM solution offering cryptographic protection, firewall, and IDS/IPS for comprehensive network security;
• Diamond ACS – control and access mediation system designed to protect information from unauthorized access;
• Dcrypt – cryptographic information protection facility.
ADVANTAGES
• Cross-platform software;
• Adaptability – TSS products can be integrated with other IT products, telecommunication systems, and security tools and can be used in virtualized environments and large networks;
• Versatility – provides required protection and high adaptability to network equipment settings by using proprietary high-performance TLS protocol;
• High performance characteristics.

Established in Moscow in 2001, Zecurion has emerged as a worldwide authority in IT security solutions, safeguarding the interests of more than 10,000 corporate clients spanning across 70+ countries. Renowned for its innovative prowess, including patented technologies, Zecurion delivers state-of-the-art products such as Zecurion Next Generation Data Loss Prevention, Zecurion Data-Centric Audit and Protection and Zecurion Secure Web Gateway. With accolades from industry leaders like Gartner and IDC, Zecurion remains at the forefront of the industry, consistently evolving to offer rapid deployment and cutting-edge solutions aimed at mitigating insider threats. 

Product portfolio includes: 
- Zecurion Next Generation Data Loss Prevention (DLP): protection against leaks;
?- Zecurion Data-Centric Audit and Protection (DCAP): protection of data at rest;
- ?Zecurion Secure Web Gateway (SWG): protection against external threats.
